 \"final parsec\nproblem\". Future observations of GRAVITY+/VLTI are expected to be able to\nspatially resolve the CB-SMBHs suggested in this paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 May 2020 00:30:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Jul 2020 09:01:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-15"}
