ced mAP and FPS score to\nmonitor the social distancing in real-time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 May 2020 10:58:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 May 2020 17:47:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 24 Apr 2021 16:15:26 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 27 Apr 2021 05:08:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-28"}
