ld which is different\nfrom the one neither of the Nehari type nor of the Pohozaev type, and then\nprove the existence of ground states. Finally under some assumptions on\n$\\omega$ and $p$, we prove that the ground state standing waves are strongly\nunstable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 May 2020 14:31:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 Jun 2020 07:01:21 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 10 Feb 2021 23:30:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-12"}
